data.description: Discover the allure of this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence nestled in a well-established community of Temple. This lovely residence is strategically priced with no HOA, presenting an excellent opportunity for first-time home (FHA) buyers searching for a move-in-ready home. Nestled in a friendly neighborhood, this property boasts a convenient and central location, providing easy access to local amenities, schools, and shopping centers. This newly listed home presents a perfect blend of comfort and style. Enhanced with upgraded flooring, the interior welcomes you with an open floor plan, fostering a cozy and inviting ambiance that is perfect for first-time home buyers seeking comfort and charm. The exterior is equally impressive, with excellent curb appeal and a private backyard with an additional patio.
